             TO  WK-H-I-LAG-CD

      *@  산업TE기업규모구분
           MOVE  WK-SYSIN-IDSTRY-CD
             TO  WK-H-I-IDSTRY-CD

      *@  한도초과년월일
           MOVE  WK-SYSIN-LIMT-YMD
             TO  WK-H-I-LIMT-YMD

